latestIgtvVideos.caption:
SIGUE SIENDO EL REY
🙏🏼🌹🇲🇽@_vicentefdez 
I grew up listening to Vicente’s music, it was played at all my family parties even my Quinceañera and cousins as well! For those that have attended any of our parties know we don’t play! Ha! Tequila shots, singing together, lots of hugs and a couple tears here and there! 🥃🫂 There will never be anyone like him and no one can sing JALISCO 🇲🇽 the way he does! (My dad’s favorite and totally makes me cry like a baby btw) 😭🤍 Sending so much love and prayers to his beautiful family. The world lost a true legend! Rest in Peace Don Vicente we love you! 🙏🏼🥃🇲🇽🤍🕊
#vicentefernandez #donchente #chente #siguesiendoelrey

latestPosts.caption:
Inspired by the 90s with a modern twist! 🥀
I’ve been thinking alot about the 90’s lately (take me back) so when we put this shoot together, I wanted to go with a lip that took me back to my high school days with a nude gloss by @doseofcolors This electric blue liner by @violette_fr has been my obsession for a while now! I always wanted to wear something like this when I was a teenager but didn’t have the guts to do it. I finally got to use it in this editorial and i’m so happy how it turned out. This blush paired with a highlight is my favorite and reminded me of one I loved back in the day @rarebeauty Joy mixed with Hope. Such a great shoot! I’m obsessed! 🤍
